⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Probability
node TTU1 · TTU1 · ⟦Probability:TTU1:1f7815⟧

WHO   — Probability — softmax · the distribution
WHAT  — Softmax turns scores into a distribution (attention weights sum to 1); the model's output is a probability distribution over the vocabulary; training minimizes a probabilistic loss.
WHERE — TTU1 · Transformer Tech Universe  Framework inputs: Attention Is All You Need (Vaswani 2017); interpretability literature; David's deck encoding  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — It is how the model chooses — softly: attention is a soft choice of where to look, generation a draw from a distribution over tokens.
HOW   — REAL — softmax, cross-entropy, sampling are genuine probability; the model is deterministic given inputs except where you sample.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I make the machine choose softly — a budget of attention divided up, a distribution over the next word, never a certainty until you sample me.

